    tv2 = ('0F0E0D0C0B0A09080706050403020100', 'BBAA9988776655443322110D', '000102030405060708090A0B0C0D0E0F101112131415161718191A1B1C1D1E1F2021222324252627', '000102030405060708090A0B0C0D0E0F101112131415161718191A1B1C1D1E1F2021222324252627', '1792A4E31E0755FB03E31B22116E6C2DDF9EFD6E33D536F1A0124B0A55BAE884ED93481529C76B6AD0C515F4D1CDD4FDAC4F02AA')
    tv3 = ((128, 128, '67E944D23256C5E0B6C61FA22FDF1EA2'), (192, 128, 'F673F2C3E7174AAE7BAE986CA9F29E17'), (256, 128, 'D90EB8E9C977C88B79DD793D7FFA161C'), (128, 96, '77A3D8E73589158D25D01209'), (192, 96, '05D56EAD2752C86BE6932C5E'), (256, 96, '5458359AC23B0CBA9E6330DD'), (128, 64, '192C9B7BD90BA06A'), (192, 64, '0066BC6E0EF34E24'), (256, 64, '7D4EA5D445501CBE'))

    def test1(self):
        key = unhexlify(b(self.tv1_key))
        for tv in self.tv1:
            nonce, aad, pt, ct = [unhexlify(b(x)) for x in tv]
            ct, mac_tag = (ct[:-16], ct[-16:])
            cipher = AES.new(key, AES.MODE_OCB, nonce=nonce)
            cipher.update(aad)
            ct2 = cipher.encrypt(pt) + cipher.encrypt()
            self.assertEqual(ct, ct2)
            self.assertEqual(mac_tag, cipher.digest())
            cipher = AES.new(key, AES.MODE_OCB, nonce=nonce)
            cipher.update(aad)
            pt2 = cipher.decrypt(ct) + cipher.decrypt()
            self.assertEqual(pt, pt2)
            cipher.verify(mac_tag)

    def test2(self):
        key, nonce, aad, pt, ct = [unhexlify(b(x)) for x in self.tv2]
        ct, mac_tag = (ct[:-12], ct[-12:])
        cipher = AES.new(key, AES.MODE_OCB, nonce=nonce, mac_len=12)
        cipher.update(aad)
        ct2 = cipher.encrypt(pt) + cipher.encrypt()
        self.assertEqual(ct, ct2)
        self.assertEqual(mac_tag, cipher.digest())
        cipher = AES.new(key, AES.MODE_OCB, nonce=nonce, mac_len=12)
        cipher.update(aad)
        pt2 = cipher.decrypt(ct) + cipher.decrypt()
        self.assertEqual(pt, pt2)
        cipher.verify(mac_tag)

    def test3(self):
        for keylen, taglen, result in self.tv3:
            result2 = algo_rfc7253(keylen, taglen, 96)
            self.assertEqual(unhexlify(b(result)), result2)